author: stsp
msg: Move resolution logic for update-move conflicts, which was spread across
two separate functions, into a single function.
No functional change intended.
* subversion/libsvn_wc/conflicts.c
(resolve_conflict_on_node): Add notify_func/notify_baton parameters.
Handle resolution of all update-move conflicts in this function.
Rework the logic a bit to clearly group the various resolution cases
supported for tree conflicts.
While here, rename the 'cancel_func_t' parameter to 'cancel_func'.
(svn_wc__mark_resolved_text_conflict,
svn_wc__mark_resolved_prop_conflicts): Pass NULL notify_func/baton pair
to resolve_conflict_on_node().
(conflict_status_walker): Remove support for update-move conflict resolution,
which has been moved to resolve_conflict_on_node().
Pass notify_func/baton pair to resolve_conflict_on_node().
